roadtrips.title: Down the East Coast
roadtrips.description: For our summer vacation of 2021, we decided to travel from our home state of Maine down to the sunshine state, Florida. We had a great time and met a lot of new people.

stops.description: Cool bride to cross with good views of the ocean.
Good pizza place near the Atlantic

comments.text: I stopped at a few places on this plan. Good time!
